  <brief_title>Study of Bortezomib (Velcade) in Combination With Dexamethasone to Treat Patients With Relapsed Hodgkin's Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of Bortezomib in Combination With Dexamethasone in Patients With Relapsed Hodgkin's Lymphoma</official_title>
