  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to evaluate wether bortezomib and dexamethasone are
      active in patients with relapsed Hodgkin's lymphoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The proteasome-inhibitor bortezomib (Velcade) shows promising activity in various human
      lymphoma cell line. In addition, several studies in heavily pretreated patients with lymphoma
      showed also promising results.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
